HEADWORD: Moonwort
<hw>Moon"wort`</hw> <pr>(m⟦oomac⟧n"w⟦ucir⟧rt`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The herb lunary or honesty. See
